data.description: This amazing all brick home is in the Spanish Trace Subdivision that is adjacent to Hidden Creek Golf Club and only minutes to the most amazing emerald waters at Navarre Beach.  There are four bedrooms and two bathrooms, a large living room with fireplace and a very spacious laundry room.  There is also a spacious bonus room for that could be used as another bedroom, a Man Cave, a craft room or as an office space.  All the appliances are new, the roof was replaced in 2021, the septic tank was pumped when seller purchased in 2021, and the hot water heater is new.
